---
title: Contact
description: Get in touch with Addison. Always happy to hear from teams hiring, devs comparing notes, and curious people.
permalink: /contact/
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block main %}

<header class="page-hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
  <h1>Get in <em style="color: var(--accent-sun);">touch</em>.</h1>
  <p class="lede">Always happy to hear from teams that are hiring, devs who want to compare notes, or anyone curious about the worlds I'm building.</p>
</header>

<section class="ct-email-block">
  <div class="ct-signal" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 80 80" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <circle cx="40" cy="40" r="18" fill="none" stroke="#FFB347" stroke-width="0.6" stroke-opacity="0.5" class="signal-ring"/>
      <circle cx="40" cy="40" r="18" fill="none" stroke="#FFB347" stroke-width="0.6" stroke-opacity="0.5" class="signal-ring-2"/>
      <circle cx="40" cy="40" r="14" fill="none" stroke="#FFB347" stroke-width="0.4" stroke-opacity="0.35"/>
      <circle cx="40" cy="40" r="9" fill="none" stroke="#FFB347" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-opacity="0.5"/>
      <circle cx="40" cy="40" r="4" fill="#FFB347"/>
      <circle cx="40" cy="40" r="2" fill="#FFE0A8"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="ct-email-text">
    <p class="ct-email-lbl">— Easiest way:</p>
    <a class="ct-email" href="mailto:addisontoscani@gmail.com">addisontoscani@gmail.com</a>
    <p class="ct-email-note">I usually reply within a few days. Sooner if it's interesting.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="rule"/>

<section class="ct-open">
  <div class="ct-open-head">
    <h2>What I'm <em style="color: var(--accent-sun);">open to</em></h2>
    <span class="eyebrow">Honest signals</span>
  </div>
  <div class="ct-open-grid">
    <div class="ct-open-item">
      <h4>Full-time roles<span class="yes">· yes</span></h4>
      <p>Small or mid-sized teams. Senior IC or tech lead. Studios that ship things they care about.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ct-open-item">
      <h4>Contract work<span class="yes">· yes</span></h4>
      <p>Defined scope, clear timeline. UE5 systems, gameplay programming, technical architecture.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ct-open-item">
      <h4>Podcasts &amp; press<span class="yes">· yes</span></h4>
      <p>Especially if you want to talk about indie devlogs, leaving a senior career, or solo development.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ct-open-item">
      <h4>"Quick chat"<span class="no">· not really</span></h4>
      <p>If it can be an email, please make it an email. Saves us both an awkward calendar dance.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="rule"/>

<section class="ct-elsewhere">
  <div class="ct-elsewhere-head">
    <h2><em style="color: var(--accent-sun);">Elsewhere</em> on the internet</h2>
    <span class="eyebrow">Other places I write &amp; share</span>
  </div>
  <div class="ct-elsewhere-grid">
    <a class="ct-place" href="https://www.youtube.com/@sporecerer" rel="me">
      <span class="name">YouTube</span>
      <span class="desc">Tutorials &amp; devlogs.<br/>Where most people find me.</span>
    </a>
    <a class="ct-place" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/addison-toscani-0b0097162/" rel="me">
      <span class="name">LinkedIn</span>
      <span class="desc">For the recruiters &amp; the prior chapter.</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

{% endblock %}
